{"tid":1354369,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：大部分人都無讀懂Trump的意思。","createTime":"2019-07-23T06:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T08:18:42.000Z","uid":2748,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb9660ecf4b7a78f69b131cb11a23ac3260d771","tid":1354369,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"陳雲：星期三的文化沙龍，我會逐個字分析特朗普的外交辭令，大部分傳媒，包括西方媒體，都沒有讀懂特朗普的意思。<br />\n劇透一句：特朗普說的，President Xi acted responsibly （習總統已經為此負了責任做事），是說 President Xi should act responsibly （習總統應該為此負責任做點事）. 說白一點，就是：請習近平總統自己把香港弄好，免得我出手不客氣。至於我如何讀到這種訊息，需要一點英文修養與《春秋》經學知識。<br />\n特朗普非常之大方得體，卻又裝作糊塗。他將香港置於阿富汗與伊朗的訪問之中，本身就已經是個幽默，甚至是威脅！<br />\n（星期三的文化沙龍，我再講清楚些。先在這裡講一點核心的，免得港共做錯事，無得回頭！元朗的鄉親父老，也要小心國際政治的變化，回頭是岸。跟大佬，要跟最大的。）"},{"pid":"3fb6068acde20935387ebd7d24463c4e38df2a21","tid":1354369,"uid":107060,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ce3a2de2df2f09d57b41d5fbdcdda7e79e3080","tid":1354369,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ed0e51552d470a5518396b17796cba56f4b2c4","tid":1354369,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"和理非新訴求-要求為《基本法》第廿二條進行本地立法，以悍衛香港自治<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354371</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"53bc078dc2310f409503e799461e413f997fe379","tid":1354369,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5242468ff278c6d86ebf8547c1b01c71bf686fe","tid":1354369,"uid":75664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"